{"tid":842111,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊練習寫中文字(1)","createTime":"2018-09-30T04:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T10:07:13.000Z","uid":8217,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd9bb4d7269617c2652646cd6a44227a100de9f","tid":842111,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"小弟一年前開始有興趣寫字<br />\n半年前開始練習多啲<br />\n<br />\n之前都有係創意台開&rdquo;你講我寫&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/125312_29db5f903bcb02d63d8c7b44cc6184b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F125312_29db5f903bcb02d63d8c7b44cc6184b9.png&h=d2590fc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/125314_07081a8006adf64815b2957ca2b051dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F125314_07081a8006adf64815b2957ca2b051dd.png&h=9119d389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為見到都有巴打有興趣練下字<br />\n<br />\n咁就不如大家一齊練習啦<br />\n<br />\n！永遠冇寫字唔靚既人，只有未開始練習既人！<br />\n！唔好同他人比較，佢只係早過你練字！<br />\n<br />\n呢度可以提字比其他人寫，又可以post自己寫既字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 互相尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4012a7a9a97762aa165340747d35fa05f884ed38","tid":842111,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推"},{"pid":"6e176343fe1feaeb1bd8a95c7685f89fd291e384","tid":842111,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c0610b39663f0ee786b2a9740dab26b0117cd01","tid":842111,"uid":198389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e176343fe1feaeb1bd8a95c7685f89fd291e384","tid":842111,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4012a7a9a97762aa165340747d35fa05f884e