islike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f2eb278ee3564099fed3e1564ab837cf09d5ba","tid":842111,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3419b49956c23bd8e46d68f2225cb920b3fe3698","tid":842111,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:39:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/001826_e8fda4ba5021de7feb48d8c2c9961591.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F001826_e8fda4ba5021de7feb48d8c2c9961591.png&h=1d3fba48&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:19:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"平時寫字會好快，要幾快有幾快<br />\n如果係練字，就會好慢<br />\n<br />\n唔會有人比人話佢寫字好快好叻，<br />\n只會有人比人話佢寫字又靚又整齊。<br />\n<br />\n所以要睇你寫字為左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/002614_ef897614ffdd125489d37d0330e35a70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F002614_ef897614ffdd125489d37d0330e35a70.png&h=e77a8ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我平時寫字真係好快"},{"pid":"c1508b3f8379d2c6df4cbfbdbf9b7a72e7ee8e57","tid":842111,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ec98480aa43329b68437917d4aa07ee535f1c66","tid":842111,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1508b3f8379d2c6df4cbfbdbf9b7a72e7ee8e57","tid":842111,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e5dec7025b58c1b94038d2dddfeef9c4ef94697","tid":842111,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"936baf578f57c0388a6c44e67004ce2bf4cde3f4","tid":842111,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:19:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"平時寫字會好快，要幾快有幾快<br />\n如果係練字，就會好慢<br />\n<br />\n唔會有人比人話佢寫字好快好叻，<br />\n只會有人比人話佢寫字又靚又整齊。<br />\n<br />\n所以要睇你寫字為左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/002614_ef897614ffdd125489d37d0330e35a70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F002614_ef897614ffdd125489d37d0330e35a70.png&h=e77a8ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我平時寫字真係好快"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:30:44.000Z","msg":"慢係冇問題，又唔係做功課同考試<br />\n如果冇力，每日拎半個鐘寫下字<br />\n一個月後，一定有進步！<br />\n<br />\n我宜家平均每日月一個鐘左右寫字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有心唔怕遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4dd21616fe35fcdc2c7d2bdbb37ee2236a5637e","tid":842111,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:32:48.000Z","msg":"你都試下寫啲字post出黎，一齊研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n互相尊重"},{"pid":"958cbf9d38ded48426555362696f4e6a8cee60f4","tid":842111,"uid":103813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"樓主點練字？  <br />\n我漫無目的咁抄文好似成效唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80f61e5f788a82b27248974b9d34003637b2a3a","tid":842111,"uid":8397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:39:49.000Z","msg":"請問巴打練字係就咁瘋狂喺白紙寫定係用格仔紙?<br />\n有冇特登臨摹一啲作品/字形?<br />\n想練字但係唔係好知點練先有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55591dd50c49df29b8f2069a8955a6fd99ecbce","tid":842111,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"我都要練字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲工作需要啲字唔可以太衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326325a3fec90b9781dc01b96d4e0b82b702bd43","tid":842111,"uid":8217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"958cbf9d38ded48426555362696f4e6a8cee60f4","tid":842111,"uid":103813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"樓主點練字？  <br />\n我漫無目的咁抄文好似成效唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:49:56.000Z","msg":"可以諗啲練習比自己，練下創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如地方名，國家<br />\n<br />\n之後follow一啲書法家，學下佢地寫字<br />\n<br />\n應該會冇咁悶，當然post啲字上黎一齊傾下都會過癮啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986b1030e2e3866f459964e584a7b8a55fec2058","tid":842111,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e80f61e5f788a82b27248974b9d34003637b2a3a","tid":842111,"uid":8397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:39:49.000Z","msg":"請問巴打練字係就咁瘋狂喺白紙寫定係用格仔紙?<br />\n有冇特登臨摹一啲作品/字形?<br />\n想練字但係唔係好知點練先有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"1, both，我認真練就用格仔紙，但練字分兩部分，質同量，格仔紙可練質。白紙/廢紙，得閒就寫，可以練力，練行氣<br />\n<br />\n2, 我平時跟小黑叔叔，阿土 Instagram<br />\n都會留意下啲書法<br />\n<br />\n3,唔洗睇效果，練得多自然好！"},{"pid":"88139c8e0d943b5fba356781c0339315223c605e","tid":842111,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d55591dd50c49df29b8f2069a8955a6fd99ecbce","tid":842111,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"我都要練字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲工作需要啲字唔可以太衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"歡迎寫字放上黎！"},{"pid":"b55610968bb8e